{
  "name": "research-analyser",
  "displayName": "Research Analyser",
  "description": "Surfaces Research Analyser output — equations, methodology, peer-review scores — directly in the editor.",
  "version": "0.7.0",
  "publisher": "kp-algomaster",
  "license": "MIT",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/kp-algomaster/Research_Analyser.git"
  },
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.85.0"
  },
  "icon": "resources/icon.png",
  "categories": ["Other"],
  "keywords": ["research", "papers", "equations", "latex", "arxiv"],
  "activationEvents": ["onStartupFinished"],
  "main": "./out/extension.js",
  "contributes": {
    "configuration": [
      {
        "title": "Server",
        "properties": {
          "researchAnalyser.apiUrl": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "http://localhost:8000",
            "description": "Base URL for the Research Analyser FastAPI backend."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.autoLoadLatestReport": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true,
            "description": "Automatically load the latest report from the API on activation."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.reportSearchPaths": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "default": ["~/ResearchAnalyserOutput", "./output"],
            "description": "Directories to search for analysis_report.json files."
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "API Keys",
        "properties": {
          "researchAnalyser.keys.openai": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "markdownDescription": "**OpenAI API Key** — used by the agentic reviewer and STORM report generator. Get yours at [platform.openai.com](https://platform.openai.com/api-keys). Stored in VS Code settings; use _Save API Keys → .env_ to write to your workspace `.env`."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.keys.google": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "markdownDescription": "**Google / Gemini API Key** — used by PaperBanana diagram generation (`gemini-2.0-flash`). Get yours at [aistudio.google.com](https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey)."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.keys.tavily": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "markdownDescription": "**Tavily API Key** — enhances related-work search in the agentic reviewer. Get yours at [tavily.com](https://app.tavily.com)."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.keys.semanticScholar": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "markdownDescription": "**Semantic Scholar API Key** — raises rate limits when fetching paper metadata. Get yours at [semanticscholar.org](https://www.semanticscholar.org/product/api)."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.keys.huggingface": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "markdownDescription": "**HuggingFace Token** — required to download MonkeyOCR and Qwen3-TTS models. Get yours at [huggingface.co/settings/tokens](https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens)."
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Editor",
        "properties": {
          "researchAnalyser.hoverEnabled": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true,
            "description": "Show LaTeX equation hover cards over known symbols."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.hoverLanguages": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "default": ["python", "typescript", "javascript", "cpp", "rust"],
            "description": "Languages for which equation hover is active."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.inlineDecorationsEnabled": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true,
            "description": "Show inline KaTeX decorations in spec.md equation block headers."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.katexFontSize": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "1em",
            "description": "Font size for KaTeX rendered equations."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.specFileGlob": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "**/{spec,*_spec}.md",
            "description": "Glob pattern for files handled by the spec.md renderer."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.insertFormat": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["comment", "docstring", "raw"],
            "default": "comment",
            "description": "Default format for inserting equations into code."
          },
          "researchAnalyser.diagramEngine": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["paperbanana", "beautiful_mermaid"],
            "default": "paperbanana",
            "markdownDescription": "**Diagram engine** to use when analysing papers.\n- `paperbanana` — AI-powered diagrams via Gemini (requires `GOOGLE_API_KEY`)\n- `beautiful_mermaid` — local Mermaid rendering (no API key needed)"
          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.analyse",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Analyse Paper",
        "icon": "$(search)"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.saveApiKeys",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Save API Keys → .env"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.openSettings",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Open Settings",
        "icon": "$(gear)"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.loadReport",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Load Report JSON"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.openPanel",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Open Report Panel"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.pickEquation",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Insert Equation"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.clearReport",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Clear Loaded Report",
        "icon": "$(clear-all)",
        "enablement": "researchAnalyser.reportLoaded"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.copyEquation",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Copy Equation (LaTeX)"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.markImplements",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Mark as Implements §…"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.fetchPaper",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Fetch Paper (arXiv / URL / DOI)",
        "icon": "$(cloud-download)"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.downloadMonkeyOcr",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Download MonkeyOCR Offline",
        "icon": "$(desktop-download)"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.startServer",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Start Backend Server",
        "icon": "$(server)"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.textToDiagrams",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Text → Diagrams",
        "icon": "$(type-hierarchy)"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.generateReview",
        "title": "Research Analyser: Generate Peer Review",
        "icon": "$(comment-discussion)"
      }
    ],
    "keybindings": [
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.analyse",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+r",
        "mac": "shift+cmd+r"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.openPanel",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+e",
        "mac": "shift+cmd+e"
      },
      {
        "command": "researchAnalyser.pickEquation",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+q",
        "mac": "shift+cmd+q",
        "when": "editorIsOpen"
      }
    ],
    "menus": {
      "editor/context": [
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.pickEquation",
          "group": "researchAnalyser@1",
          "when": "editorIsOpen && researchAnalyser.reportLoaded"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.markImplements",
          "group": "researchAnalyser@2",
          "when": "editorIsOpen && researchAnalyser.reportLoaded"
        }
      ],
      "view/item/context": [
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.copyEquation",
          "when": "viewItem == equation"
        }
      ],
      "view/title": [
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.analyse",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.textToDiagrams",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "group": "navigation@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.clearReport",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar && researchAnalyser.reportLoaded",
          "group": "navigation@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.startServer",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "group": "overflow@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.downloadMonkeyOcr",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "group": "overflow@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.openSettings",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "group": "overflow@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.fetchPaper",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "group": "overflow@4"
        },
        {
          "command": "researchAnalyser.generateReview",
          "when": "view == researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "group": "overflow@5"
        }
      ]
    },
    "viewsContainers": {
      "activitybar": [
        {
          "id": "researchAnalyser",
          "title": "Research Analyser",
          "icon": "resources/activity-bar-icon.svg"
        }
      ]
    },
    "views": {
      "researchAnalyser": [
        {
          "id": "researchAnalyser.sidebar",
          "name": "Research Context",
          "when": "true"
        }
      ]
    },
    "viewsWelcome": [
      {
        "view": "researchAnalyser.sidebar",
        "contents": "📄 **Analyse a Paper**\nFetch and analyse from arXiv, DOI, URL, or local PDF.\n[$(search) Analyse Paper](command:researchAnalyser.analyse)\n[$(cloud-download) Fetch Paper (arXiv / URL)](command:researchAnalyser.fetchPaper)\n\n🎨 **Generate Diagrams**\nCreate publication-quality methodology, architecture, and results diagrams from text.\n[$(type-hierarchy) Text → Diagrams](command:researchAnalyser.textToDiagrams)\n\n📋 **Review & Report**\nGenerate agentic peer review with Stanford scoring.\n[$(comment-discussion) Generate Peer Review](command:researchAnalyser.generateReview)\n[$(folder-opened) Load Existing Report](command:researchAnalyser.loadReport)\n\n⚙️ **Setup**\n[$(server) Start Backend Server](command:researchAnalyser.startServer)\n[$(desktop-download) Download MonkeyOCR Offline](command:researchAnalyser.downloadMonkeyOcr)\n[$(gear) Open Settings & API Keys](command:researchAnalyser.openSettings)",
        "when": "!researchAnalyser.reportLoaded"
      }
    ],
    "customEditors": [
      {
        "viewType": "researchAnalyser.specRenderer",
        "displayName": "Spec Renderer (KaTeX)",
        "selector": [
          { "filenamePattern": "**/spec.md" },
          { "filenamePattern": "**/*_spec.md" }
        ],
        "priority": "option"
      }
    ]
  },
  "scripts": {
    "build": "node esbuild.config.js",
    "watch": "node esbuild.config.js --watch",
    "lint": "eslint src --ext .ts",
    "test": "node ./out/tests/runTests.js",
    "package": "vsce package",
    "vscode:prepublish": "npm run build"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/katex": "^0.16.7",
    "@types/mocha": "^10.0.6",
    "@types/node": "20.x",
    "@types/sinon": "^17.0.3",
    "@types/vscode": "^1.85.0",
    "@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin": "^7.0.0",
    "@typescript-eslint/parser": "^7.0.0",
    "@vscode/test-electron": "^2.3.9",
    "@vscode/vsce": "^2.24.0",
    "esbuild": "^0.21.0",
    "eslint": "^8.57.0",
    "mocha": "^10.3.0",
    "sinon": "^17.0.1",
    "typescript": "^5.4.0"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "katex": "^0.16.10"
  }
}
